# mbsyncrc based on
# http://pragmaticemacs.com/emacs/migrating-from-offlineimap-to-mbsync-for-mu4e/
# and
# http://www.ict4g.net/adolfo/notes/2014/12/27/EmacsIMAP.html
IMAPAccount devnulllabs
AuthMechs GSSAPI, CRAM-MD5, PLAIN, LOGIN
Host mail.runbox.com
User kballou%devnulllabs.io
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
PipelineDepth 1

IMAPStore devnulllabs-remote
Account devnulllabs

MaildirStore devnulllabs-local
Path ~/.mail/
Inbox ~/.mail/INBOX

Channel devnulllabs-inbox
Master :devnulllabs-remote:
Slave :devnulllabs-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel devnulllabs-sent
Master :devnulllabs-remote:"Sent"
Slave :devnulllabs-local:"sent"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel devnulllabs-archive
Master :devnulllabs-remote:"Archives"
Slave :devnulllabs-local:"archive"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel devnulllabs-trash
Master :devnulllabs-remote:"Trash"
Slave :devnulllabs-local:"trash"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel devnulllabs-spam
Master :devnulllabs-remote:"Spam"
Slave :devnulllabs-local:"spam"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel devnulllabs-lists
Master :devnulllabs-remote:"lists"
Slave :devnulllabs-local:"lists"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group devnulllabs
Channel devnulllabs-inbox
Channel devnulllabs-sent
Channel devnulllabs-archive
Channel devnulllabs-trash
Channel devnulllabs-lists
